      "comment": "Pluralization key for \"meeting\". The argument is the string “Tap the blob to analyze your day.”, the string “Tap the blob to load today's energy.”, the string “Tap the blob to start your first check-in.”, the string “Your data stays private on this device.”, the string “Ready when you are.”, the string “Loading…”, the string “based on sleep, movement, stress, and calendar load”, the string “Each row shows what that signal actually added or removed today.”, the string “Sleep”, the string “Recovery”, the string “Heart at rest”, the string “Movement”, the string “Stress”, the string “Calendar”, the string “Workout effort”, the string “no data”, the string “calm all day”, the string “no meetings”, the string “solid rest”, the string “okay rest”, the string “short night”, the string “well recovered”, the string “moderate recovery”, the string “still tired”, the string “calm at rest”, the string “a little elevated”, the string “working hard at rest”, the string “1 meeting”, the string “komo couldn't read your sleep data last night.”, the string “make sure your Apple Watch or iPhone is charging nearby while you sleep.”, the string “try to be in bed 45 minutes earlier tonight to recover.”, the string “a 15-minute nap this afternoon or an earlier bedtime tonight would help.”, the string “you're rested. maybe use that good energy on something you care about.”, the string “a 10-minute walk right now would reset your body and your focus.”, the string “try a short walk before your next task to hit 5,000.”, the string “you moved a lot. let the evening be for rest, not another big effort.”, the string “your body seems tired today. recovery looks lower than usual.”, the string “your body recovered well. you have good energy reserves today.”, the string “keep today light and protect your sleep tonight.”, the string “this is a good window for a workout or deep focus work.”, the string “your heart is working a bit harder than usual at rest.”, the string “your heart